PAUSED placeholder per ADR 2026-05-18-agent-shape-11-file-contract.md.

To pause Stet runtime: `touch ~/.hermes/profiles/stet/PAUSED` (or
`touch ~/Projects/agents/hermes/profiles/stet/PAUSED` if running from repo).

To resume: `rm` that PAUSED file.

This `.template` file is the placeholder so lint passes; the real
`PAUSED` file (without `.template`) is the kill-switch sentinel.
